args: It is an honor to meet you, Cecile.\nI am Vice Captain Patia of the\nWhite Sparrow Corps.
A female knight came to my house the other day.\nAnd that...was how I died.
...I'm still alive? Oh wow. I guess that\nknight must have been a dream.
Oh, thank the Goddess you're awake!
Are you still feeling unwell, Cecile?
No! You're just the first female knight\nI've seen in a long time, and it sort of...\nreopened some old wounds.
You're wounded?! Let me see. I know first\naid, and as a knight sworn to protect the\npeople, I will see you healed!
A knight... Protecting the people...\nAAAAUUUGH! NO MOOOOORE!
...Yes, I see now. You were speaking of\npsychological wounds and not injuries to\nflesh and bone.
Pretty much. See, after Dyrenell took over,\nI killed dragons and brought suffering to\nthe people.
Yet despite all that, I didn't save a thing.\nNot my king, not my people, and not my\npride as a knight or my ideals.
So whenever I'm around people who still\nespouse that kind of chivalry and idealism,\nit feels like my heart is...breaking.
I had no idea. Pray forgive my careless\nindiscretion, Cecile.
I'm the one who should be apologizing.\nYou were looking after me, and I just\nfreaked out and started screaming.

Don't spare it a second though. Besides,
if there is anyone to blame here, it is
clearly Captain Leif for not informing me
of the situation beforehand.
How could a leader be so inconsiderate?
Heh. Sounds like Leif's really running you\nthrough the wringer.
Hey, so why did you come to my\nplace anyway?
Oh, apologies! Captain Leif sent me here\nto see if you have an answer for him.
He wanted to know whether you'd given\nany more thought to joining forces with\nus in New Alberia.
I admit to giving the matter a good deal\nof thought since I met with him again.
If I can't face my past, I'll never be able to\nmake up for all of the pain I caused the\npeople and dragons in my homeland.
So I want to put in the work. I want to\ngo back to the person I used to be and\nrediscover what it means to be a knight.
I do. But, um, I don't really know how to\nstart...or even where I'm going.
Then first things first. I, Patia, shall escort\nyou safely to the Halidom!
I swear this on my honor as a\nWhite Sparrow!
Pray forgive me! Have I reopened an old\nwound of one kind or another?
We're good. Just a knee-jerk reaction\nthat I need to learn how to overcome.
Oh man, I'm not dealing well at all here...\nI need something to get me through this.
Manachew is a mana-infused supplement,\nyes? Does it truly help you feel better?
Oh, you bet! It's the BEST, plus it works in\na heartbeat! You wanna try? C'mon, try it!
Well, I admit to being a tad curious...\n*nibble* Ouch! Hmm... *nibble*
Well? Pretty sweet, eh?! Really perks you\nright up? Sure it does!
I fear I feel the same as before.
(Why doesn't this stuff ever work on\nanyone but me?)
